    <item>
      <title>印度选举：计票正在进行中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-04/india-elections-vote-counting-underway-across-country-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过长达六周的马拉松式选举，印度的计票工作已经开始。计票工作由印度选举委员会在全国各地的中心进行，首先检查邮寄选票。最终结果预计将于周二公布。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-04/india-elections-vote-counting-underway-across-country-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 03:08:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度股市和卢比下跌，早期计票结果显示莫迪胜选可能性较小</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/india-s-stock-futures-rise-as-investors-await-election-result</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度股市周二下跌，逆转了推动主要股指创下历史新高的涨势，卢比和债券也走弱，因为最初的领先优势表明总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的印度人民党将以微弱优势获胜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/india-s-stock-futures-rise-as-investors-await-election-result</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 01:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 计划引发对供应充足的担忧，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 OPEC+ 计划比预期更早地将石油返回市场引发对供应过剩的担忧之后，油价从近四个月来的最低结算价延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 23:30:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
